{"type": "article", "id": 22106, "title": "在聚会上总忍不住打开手机来刷，是病", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 998, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">但是根本无药可救啊！</p>\n<p>虽然我们特别理解你只想在家享受假日废柴状态的心情，但是难得聚会，还是走出与手机的独处，看看这个世界吧？</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606002148EQ8PD1j4t2mcU0oG.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>我们准备了一些应用，如果非要在聚会的时候玩手机，就和你的朋友们一起来点有意思的呗。</p>\n<p class=\"\">祝开心！</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图来自 Friends，插图来自 <a href=\"http://giphy.com/gifs/arianagrande-ariana-grande-music-video-focus-xT77XWjBlkyG2yLlMA\">Giphy</a></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n\n"}